====================
pluma-plugins 1.16.0
====================

Port to GTK+3.
Fix trivial deprecations; GtkAction and GtkUIManager still remain.
Disable python plugins until libpeas-based Pluma 1.18.

===================
pluma-plugins 1.8.0
===================

Port to gsettings.
Port back to libgucharmap.
Disable terminal plugin until Pluma is ported to gobject-introspection.

===================
pluma-plugins 1.4.0
===================

Port to libmucharmap.

===================
pluma-plugins 1.2.0
===================

Initial release, based on gedit-plugins 2.32.0.
